               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <subc>III,1</subc> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> dissipari </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> discuti </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> desquamari </t:quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወተሥዕዐ፡ እምብንተ፡ አዕይንቲሁ፡ ዝኩ፡ ጢስ፡</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἐλεπίσθη</foreign> <ref cRef="Tob." loc="11,12">Tob. 11,12</ref>; item in actis <ref cRef="Tobiae Sx. Masc." loc="16">Tobiae Sx. Masc. 16</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተሥዕዐ፡ እምአዕይንቲሁ፡ ከመ፡ ዘሣሬት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Act." loc="9,18">Act. 9,18</ref> Platt. – <lbl expand="Vocabularium Aethiopicum, -a -a">Voc. Ae.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተሥዕዐ፡ ብ፡ ተገረፈ፡ ተቀሥፈሂ፡ ይ፡</foreign> </sense>
               
            <sense xml:id="Tmain" xml:lang="en" source="#traces"> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">taśǝʿǝʿa</t:quote></cit>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተስዕዐ፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">tasǝʿǝʿa</t:quote></cit> <sense n="G" xml:id="TG"> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተሥዕዐ፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">taśǝʿǝʿa</t:quote></cit> <subc>III,1</subc> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይሠዓዕ፡</foreign> «<cit type="translation" xml:lang="fr"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">laisser tomber des écailles</t:quote></cit> (provenant des yeux)» ― <foreign xml:lang="am">ክርፍርፍ፡ አለ፡</foreign> Ms. <ref type="BM" target="BNFabb217">BNFabb217</ref>, fol. 53v. <lb/>
 Voici le texte des Actes des Apòtres où figure le verbe <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተሥዕዐ፡</foreign>; ce texte se rapporte à la guérison de la cécité de saint Paul: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሖረ፡ ሐናንያ፡ ወቦአ፡ ቤቶ፡ ወወደየ፡ እዴሁ፡ ዲቤሁ። ወይቤሎ፡ ሳውል፡ እኁየ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ፈነወኒ፡ ኀቤከ፡ ዘአስተርአየከ፡ በፍኖት፡ እንዘ፡ ትመጽእ፡ ከመ፡ ትርአይ፡ ወይምላእ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ላዕሌከ። ወሶቤሃ፡ ተሥዕዓ፡ እምአዕይንቲሁ፡ ከመ፡ ዘሳሬት፡ ወተከሥታ፡ አዕይንቶሁ፡ ወርእየ፡ ሶቤሃ።</foreign> Actes, IX, 17–18. <lb/>
